definitions.definition: ( biblical ) The son of Obed and the father of king David .
A male given name from Hebrew of biblical origin.
A female given name , variant of Jessie .

main_definition: ( biblical ) The son of Obed and the father of king David .

definitions.definition: A representation of the genealogy of Christ , in decorative art , such as a genealogical tree in stained glass or a branched candlestick .
